Shih has received several awards for her achievements, including recognition as a Young Global Leader by the World Economic Forum,[11] the Fortune 40 Under 40 (2012),[12] and the Ad Age 40 Under 40 (2012).[13]
Personal life[edit]
Shih is currently married to health-tech entrepreneur Daniel Chao. They live in San Francisco, California.[14]
