Clara Shih - Wikipedia





















 






Clara Shih

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Clara Shih


Born
Clara Chung-wai Shih
(1982-01-11) January 11, 1982 (age 35)[1]
Hong Kong


